---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout title="MealMap — Terms of Use" description="MealMap terms of use and EULA.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <a href="/" class="text-white/30 hover:text-white text-sm transition mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1">
      ← Back to Home
    </a>
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">Terms of Use — MealMap</h1>
    <p class="text-white/30 mb-10">Last updated: March 26, 2026</p>

    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">By downloading, installing, or using MealMap ("the App"), you agree to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, do not use the App.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">1. Description of Service</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">MealMap is a meal planning application that provides meal calendar management, recipe storage, grocery list generation, and AI-powered features including Chef AI chat, Snap to Meal photo recognition, and Auto Plan weekly meal generation. The App is developed by Justin Bundrick / BunjiSolutions.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">2. Subscriptions & Payment</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">MealMap offers a free tier with limited features and optional premium subscriptions:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li><strong class="text-white/80">Monthly:</strong> $4.99/month, billed monthly</li>
      <li><strong class="text-white/80">Annual:</strong> $29.99/year, billed annually (save 50%)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Payment is charged to your Apple ID account upon confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage and cancel subscriptions in your Apple ID Account Settings. No refunds are provided for unused portions of a subscription period.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">3. AI Features</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">AI-powered features (Chef AI, Snap to Meal, Auto Plan) use third-party AI services to generate responses. AI-generated content including recipes, meal suggestions, and ingredient lists are provided for informational purposes only. We do not guarantee the accuracy, safety, or nutritional correctness of AI-generated content. Always use your own judgment when preparing food, especially regarding allergies, dietary restrictions, and food safety.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>You are responsible for verifying any AI-generated recipes or nutritional information</li>
      <li>You must not use AI features for any illegal, harmful, or abusive purpose</li>
      <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your device and data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">The App, its design, code, and content are the property of Justin Bundrick / BunjiSolutions. Recipes you create or import are yours. AI-generated content does not confer intellectual property rights to either party.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">The App is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of the App, including but not limited to: allergic reactions, food safety issues, or inaccurate nutritional information from AI-generated content.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">7. Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:justinbundrick@gmail.com" class="text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 underline">justinbundrick@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>
</Layout>
